# id: PropertiesUtil -> public static long getLong(Properties config, String key, long defaultValue)
commentText: Get long from properties._This method throws an exception if the long is not valid.__@param config Properties_@param key key in Properties_@param defaultValue default value if value is not set_@return default or value of key_@throws IllegalArgumentException
codeText: public static long getLong(Properties config, String key, long defaultValue) {_		String val = config.getProperty(key)__		if (val == null) {_			return defaultValue__		} else {_			try {_				return Long.parseLong(val)__			} catch (NumberFormatException nfe) {_				throw new IllegalArgumentException("Value for configuration key='" + key + "' is not set correctly. " +_						"Entered value='" + val + "'. Default value='" + defaultValue + "'")__			}_		}_	}
